other join the battle, now it was 9 agianst 7. A bit difficult but it could 
all be handled with stratigy. Turning, he saw Gremlin already firing at some 
of the Nightmare group, and Hell Beast joined too.

         Aerostreak frowned at Quasar, obviously she seemed to be knowing 
what she was doing. "Alright, sorry. Just lets shows these rebles who there 
dealing with!"
